 <span data-ttu-id="d8eef-194">下面的示例创建一个名为的规则 `winnerRule` ，然后创建一个 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 名为的对象 `document` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8eef-194">The following example creates a rule named `winnerRule`, and then creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object named `document`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d8eef-195">然后，该示例调用 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> 方法将规则添加到文档中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8eef-195">The example then calls the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> method to add the rule to the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d8eef-196">最后，该示例将文档的 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Root%2A> 属性设置为 `winnerRule` ，从而使其成为 `root rule` 由对象定义的语法 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8eef-196">Finally, the example sets the document's <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Root%2A> property to `winnerRule`, thereby making it the `root rule` for the grammar defined by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object.</span></span>  
  
